{# ===================== WHAT MAKES FULL SUPPLY SO DIFFERENT? ===================== #}
{% call section(tone="tan", narrow=true) %}
  {{ sectionHead("What makes Full Supply so different?", center=true) }}
  <p>Our founder, Connie, launched Full Supply as a mentoring process designed exclusively for women. Using a strong Biblical foundation paired with a caring relational approach, our process guides women to grow, build and lead other women well.</p>
  <p>When women go through the Full Supply training and mentoring programs, they become confident believers ready to lead, mentor and shape future leaders for Christ.</p>
  <p>Discover the difference mentoring makes&hellip;</p>
  <p>{{ button("Schedule a Call", scheduleUrl, variant="accent", size="lg", attrs='target="_blank" rel="noopener"') }}</p>
{% endcall %}
